    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Would it be possible to have 2 functions in `vim.lsp.diagnostic` for populating the quickfix window with the buffer or workspace diagnostics? It would probably also be nice to have an option for the diagnostics handler to continuously populate the quickfix window as well, though that will probably not be very useful, since it will overwrite other usages of that window.\r\n\r\nEdit: there'a already a function for setting the buffer diagnostics in a location list. So I'd like to have the equivalent function for setting the workspace diagnostics in a location list as well.",
